Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------- ED ---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:24.07,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:27.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:31.52,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up your brain!Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:34.10,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:40.26,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“谛め”がくれた 安楽沈滞の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.62,0:22:46.54,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつからだっただろう？ふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:49.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,変わらずにいてと愿うこと-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:53.45,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,変わりゆく时に生きる仆ら-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:56.63,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の声を…言い得ぬ梦を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:23:00.64,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君と繋がった空へ　响かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.91,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと强く…この両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:08.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:11.50,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“今度こそは…”つぶやく今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:14.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤さえも无駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:17.97,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと早く…君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:21.35,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たとえ羽が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:24.62,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪む世界　走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.72,0:23:27.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覚のその向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:33.39,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真実”と　加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:24.07,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:27.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:31.52,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up your brain!Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:34.10,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:40.26,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放棄」所帶給我的 安樂但停滯的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.62,0:22:46.54,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知從什麼時候開始  突然間開始變得閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:49.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈望永恆不變的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:53.45,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不斷改變地世界生存的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:56.63,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心聲…無法說出夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:23:00.64,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響徹著 這與你相連的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.91,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果更用力地…用你的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:08.23,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我揮去所有的淚水的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:11.50,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將永不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:14.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這些傷痕也不會讓它白費
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:17.97,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更快地 前往你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:21.35,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這雙翅膀被撕裂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:24.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要奔出 這扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.72,0:23:27.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著我所感受到的彼方前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:33.39,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我的「真實」去加速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------- ED ---------------------
